            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Signum <lb n="2"/>dei Neptuni iussu <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>aris</ex></expan> <del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> Messi</del> <lb n="4"/><del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> Traiani Deci</del> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>F</abbr><ex>elicis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pont</abbr><ex>ificis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>tr</abbr><ex>ibunicia</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>pot</abbr><ex>estate</ex></expan> III co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulis</ex></expan> II proco<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>res publica <lb n="8"/>Aquileiensium <lb n="9"/>restituit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Reliefs: auf der linken Nebenseite ein urceus, auf der rechten eine patera. Auf der Oberseite Einlassung (für eine Plinthe?). Datierung: circa September bis 31. Dezember(?) 250 n. Chr. (trib. pot. III des Decius). (B): AE 1982: Z. 5: p(ontificis) max(imi) trib(unicia).</p>
            </div>
